provider.name: Wells Fargo
provider.loginHelp:
To log in successfully, please ensure following conditions are satisfied for your username at Wells Fargo.
Your Username:

  1. Must be 6 to 14 characters in length and including at least one letter.
  2. Cannot contain 9 or more numbers
  3. Must not contain Special Characters other than hyphens (-) or underscores (_)
  4. Must be different than your password, ATM PIN, or Social Security number, and not easy for others to guess!

Get all your Fidelity accounts here.
In case you have any Fidelity missing account or unable to link your Fidelity account, we request you to ensure following conditions are satisfied-

Once confirmed, please add your Fidelity account or perform a refresh by Edit Credentials

If you have VIP Access Code set up,
Please wait to enter the VIP Access Code (OTP) if set up and prompted.

provider.name: E*TRADE
provider.help:
If you are a registered user and use a security token:

  1. Enter your registered user ID and password.
  2. Select Password and Token from the drop-down menu.
    • A pop up appears
  3. Enter your security code
If you are a registered user but do not use a security token:
  1. Enter your user ID and password
  2. Select Password Only option the drop-down menu.

provider.name: Huntington Bank (Personal)
provider.loginHelp:
To login successfully,Please grant third-party financial management tools access to your Huntington account(s) as follows-

  1. Log-in to huntington.com
  2. Select the Customer Service tab on the top menu
  3. Under My Information, select Allow Financial Management Tools Access
  4. Review the Terms and Conditions
  5. Select the On Option
  6. Click Save

provider.name: UBS Wealth Management
provider.help:
For Successful Aggregation, Please call the UBS Customer care [888-279-3343 (US customers) & 201-352-5257 (Non-US customers)] and follow the instructions.
[OR]

  1. Login to UBS site
  2. Provide your login credentials.
  3. Click on \"Profile Settings\"
  4. Then Click Enroll for Account Aggregation Services\"
  5. Then click on \"Enroll\" for the aggregator \"Yodlee\"
  6. You will then need to provide the \"Website Login Credentials\" and \"accept\" the terms and conditions on that page.

USAA
provider.help:
To log in successfully, please follow instructions as below:

Cybercode Token users
Users who have enrolled for the option of cybercode token at your bank, please fill in below fields

  1. Enter Online ID
  2. Enter dummy value in password field
  3. Enter your PIN in pin field


Cybercode Text users
Users who have enrolled for the option of cybercode text at your bank, please fill in below fields

  1. Enter Online ID
  2. Enter your Password in password field
  3. Enter dummy value in pin field


Remaining users who have neither opted for \"Cybercode Token\" nor \"Cybercode Text\" at your bank, please fill in your Online ID, Password and PIN in the login form.
